snippet.title: Atomic Bomberman gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Atomic Bomberman, PC game produced by Interplay in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/atomic-bomberman/1872/
Playing several matches against another AI player and against 4 AI players. Game allows network multiplayer.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Tank Wars - https://youtu.be/Mv96a7sj6Pg
Bombs and Bugs - https://youtu.be/WJbQgS8QIHY
KartRace - https://youtu.be/FK3aumfd62U
